WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.078
Diagnostic workup starts with ECG, troponin,

00:00:03.078 --> 00:00:04.617
and natriuretic peptides.

00:00:04.617 --> 00:00:07.696
Echocardiography reveals wall motion abnormalities and

00:00:07.696 --> 00:00:08.209
effusions.

00:00:08.209 --> 00:00:11.287
Cardiac MRI — applying the Lake

00:00:11.287 --> 00:00:14.365
Louise criteria of myocardial edema plus

00:00:14.365 --> 00:00:17.443
late gadolinium enhancement — is the

00:00:17.443 --> 00:00:18.983
noninvasive gold standard.

00:00:18.983 --> 00:00:22.061
Endomyocardial biopsy remains definitive for refractory

00:00:22.061 --> 00:00:23.600
or giant-cell cases.
